\par\pard\plain \tx0\li360\fi360\sa120\sl262\slmult1\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf7 In this scene, there is a subtle hint that Evan\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s health may not be as good as it seems. In this book, Evan is healthy and has no illness diagnosis.}
